<collectingCountry id="F3197604FFFBFFBEFC35FCEFFB165614" box="[1008,1185,857,882]" name="New Caledonia" pageId="1" pageNumber="389">New Caledonia</collectingCountry>
. After the study of the CSCA material, two female specimens of this species from 
<collectingCountry id="F3197604FFFBFFBEFC8AFCCBFBB756F0" box="[847,1024,893,918]" name="New Caledonia" pageId="1" pageNumber="389">New Caledonia</collectingCountry>
