<taxonomicName id="4C0E4D17FFFBFFBEFECDFC17FE0056DC" box="[264,439,929,954]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Citrogramma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="389" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="asombrosum">
<emphasis id="B97AEA86FFFBFFBEFECDFC17FE0056DC" box="[264,439,929,954]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="389">C. asombrosum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is given below.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
