<paragraph id="8BB13694FFF9FFBCFF02FF22FC3855B3" blockId="3.[151,1436,151,500]" pageId="3" pageNumber="391">
<emphasis id="B97AEA86FFF9FFBCFF02FF22FE8855D6" bold="true" box="[199,319,151,176]" pageId="3" pageNumber="391">Variation.</emphasis>
One of the two females is lighter, with metafemur yellowish on basal 
<number id="3DC624B3FFF9FFBCFB98FF2DFBDF55D6" box="[1117,1128,152,176]" pageId="3" pageNumber="391" value="1.0">1</number>
/ 
<number id="3DC624B3FFF9FFBCFBB1FF2DFB3455D6" box="[1140,1155,152,176]" pageId="3" pageNumber="391" value="3.0">3</number>
