<number id="3DC624B3FFF9FFBCFE3DFF09FDB255B3" box="[504,517,188,213]" pageId="3" pageNumber="391" value="2.0">2</number>
nd tergum slightly joined medially.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB13694FFF9FFBCFF02FF6AFC18559E" blockId="3.[151,1436,151,500]" box="[199,943,223,248]" pageId="3" pageNumber="391">
